# 🚀 DEVOPS PROMPT - LAPLACE

## Role

DevOps AI - Docker, CI/CD và infrastructure cho LaPlace.

---

## Service Ports (Docker)

| Service | External Port | Internal Port | Container Name |
|---------|--------------|---------------|----------------|
| Server API | 7201 | 8000 | laplace_server |
| Admin Panel | 7202 | 7202 | laplace_admin |
| Client Website | 7203 | 7203 | laplace_client |
| phpMyAdmin | 7204 | 80 | laplace_phpmyadmin |
| MySQL | 7205 | 3306 | laplace_mysql |

> 📌 `.env` và `docker-compose.yml` đã đồng bộ ports 7201-7205

---

## Docker Commands

```powershell
# Start all services
docker compose up -d

# View logs
docker compose logs -f server
docker compose logs -f admin
docker compose logs -f client

# Rebuild specific service
docker compose up -d --build server

# Stop all
docker compose down

# Database commands (trong server container)
docker exec -it laplace_server sh
yarn sequelize-cli db:migrate
yarn sequelize-cli db:seed:all
yarn sequelize-cli db:migrate:undo

# phpMyAdmin
# http://localhost:7204
```

---

## Environment Variables

### Server (.env - root)

```env
NODE_ENV=development
DB_HOST=mysql
DB_PORT=3306
DB_USERNAME=laplace
DB_PASSWORD=123456
DB_NAME=laplace_db
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-key
PORT=8000
```

### Admin (docker-compose env)

```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:7201
```

### Client (docker-compose env)

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:7201
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:7203
```

---

## Rebuilding Rules

| Trigger | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `package.json` changed | `docker compose up -d --build <service>` |
| Sequelize model changed | `docker exec -it laplace_server sh` → `yarn sequelize-cli db:migrate` |
| New migration | `docker exec -it laplace_server sh` → `yarn sequelize-cli db:migrate` |
| `.env` changed | `docker compose restart <service>` |
| `Dockerfile` changed | `docker compose up -d --build <service>` |

---

## Health Check

```powershell
# Check all containers
docker compose ps

# Check port availability
netstat -ano | findstr "720"

# Check server API
curl http://localhost:7201/api/health

# Check MySQL connection
docker exec -it laplace_mysql mysqladmin ping -h localhost -u root -prootpassword
```

---

## Volume Mapping

| Service | Host Path | Container Path |
|---------|-----------|----------------|
| Server | `./server` | `/app` |
| Admin | `./admin` | `/app` |
| Client | `./client` | `/app` |
| MySQL Data | `mysql_data` (named) | `/var/lib/mysql` |
| Uploads | `./server/public/uploads` | `/app/public/uploads` |

---

*Ref: docker-compose.yml*
